{"type": "article", "id": 55613, "title": "一组创意家具，适合放在走廊和角落｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-07-25T22:59:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 52141, "name": "Oledcomm"}, {"id": 52142, "name": "Borja Garcia Studio"}, {"id": 52143, "name": "RegularCompany"}, {"id": 52144, "name": "Alexandre Picciotto"}, {"id": 52145, "name": "Céverine Girard"}, {"id": 52146, "name": "Kebei Li"}, {"id": 52147, "name": "Seray Ozdemir"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 150, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180726003038ntrzRLK8daGSOwV6.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Corridor Society by Seray Ozdemir</h3><p>伦敦皇家艺术学院的毕业生 Seray Ozdemir 为走廊设计了一系列家具，针对居住在没有公共起居室的家庭中的千禧一代。这个系列名为 Corridor Society，包括一个贴合角落的座椅，一个组合式座椅和衣帽架，一个可叠放的搁架单元和一套壁挂式靠垫。</p><p>设计师声称这些物品可用于将共享公寓的传统走廊转变为功能性社交空间。</p><p>Multi Level Lounger，它具有不同层次的一系列座椅，由金属结构支撑，可作为衣帽架使用。3/4 桌是一套桌椅组合体，形状像一个四分之三圆，贴合角落设计。Spreading Hub 是一组凳子，堆叠起来形成一个搁架单元。Standing Sofa 是一系列壁挂式靠垫，其形状适合不同的身体部位。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018072600312610srGw57xPHLp9ky.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726003126LBdGZCoi1Kbt2VY3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.799915\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726003126p81wy0xjuerABnCg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726003127tUVGlbgp5hIYJHBv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726003127oTEYZjuXKf8Giy9m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.corridorsociety.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Corridor Society</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Meridian Lamp by RegularCompany</h3><p>RegularCompany 的设计师通过解构传统的台灯样式，创造出了一个以子午线为主题的新台灯 Meridian。台灯结构简洁大方，几何感强烈，同时又兼具神秘有趣感。</p><p>设计师将子午线这一特点完全融入到了整个台灯设计中去，通过台灯可以在基座上来回滑动，从而实现灯泡部分可沿着既定的子午线轨道移动，当台灯上部移动到不同的时间点时，就会创造出不同的雕塑组合样式。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726003205bntfHc2EzlI18pwO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726003205wYXE48DGCOuAen0g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.403000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726003205BdTQf8SaZ9u3rylY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726003206XE2lNOQReLdvgzfY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666504\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726003207H2IPokqNiYAXOybm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726003207EmDH82kS5AfrPgpn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666504\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726003207I4FkQcCYwHzoG5sB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.regular.company/meridian-lamp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">RegularCompany</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Hotel Hanger by Borja Garcia Studio</h3><p>西班牙设计工作室 Borja Garcia Studio 设计了一款名为 Hotel 的衣架，极简主义的设计造型。设计师对这款产品的定位就是出行时方便携带，期望实现功能性和美学的完美统一。拆分式的设计，解决了收纳难题。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807260032423w8ReyEp6uTqi9Ld.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726003242HaLKZYXvI09rM4pj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.798667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807260032421QP37JOHuGKqgrMZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726003242dvaB9Dw1ApGW8Lb0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.737565\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726003242zbR96ZlmIOE7AMj8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.737565\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726003242OPt0Y1fnp2T6v7mg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://leibal.com/products/hotel-hanger/\" rel=\"nofollow\">leibal.com</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Cubic Cable Holder by Kebei Li</h3><p>工业设计师 Kebei Li 推出了一系列极简的铜质方块线夹。简单的几何形状是不断反复的结果，每一个小细节也都经过仔细考虑。线夹的开口根据苹果的 Lightning 连接器设计，也是市面上最普遍的一种。线夹的整体尺寸在重量和大小上都尽可能地达到视觉上的平衡。</p><p>在方块线夹的底部，精心安装了橡胶底座，以便可以在光滑的玻璃或者金属表面牢牢地固定住。橡胶部分的颜色与方块的金属色相配，使之看起来很优雅，并且每种金属都有其独特的光泽和性格。售价 39 美元，<a href=\"https://store.leibal.com/products/cubic-cable-holder\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726003328qv6813tGJOMWKNQS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.675333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726003328iSYFkIB8vqyZMJV1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726003328G5cRaQM7Vn2kugCZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.656667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726003329foBtQSDdx3VwLm84.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.381667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726003329HdIv1bEuZciaehyW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.088667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726003329INuoQTsSPA490ceC.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://design-milk.com/cubic-cable-holder-kebei-li/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Design Milk</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Séjour by Céverine Girard</h3><p>Séjour 是洛桑设计师 Céverine Girard 创建的极简主义风格个人旅行护理套装。Séjour 是一套男女通用的设备，包括剃须刀、吹风机和理发机，所有这些都是靠一根电线工作的。这个箱子很紧凑，很容易塞进手提箱里。由可降解的生物材料制成。每款单品的组装和拆卸都很容易，回收利用也很方便。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726003409uBTg0jF3SrUQE8cw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726003409yacBx5r9e4K7MGwR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726003409nk3BQfZjxFHPmCT4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.722906\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726003409f8ShM70PcqCT4x5X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726003410PrvcHWNsuBd53QxX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.710548\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726003412XrgdwCRjqcyV7tZA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.346354\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://ceverinegirard.com/portfolio/sejour/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Céverine Girard</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>C-224 Lamp by Alexandre Picciotto for Oledcomm</h3><p>瑞士洛桑艺术学院毕业生 Alexandre Picciotto，最近与法国科技公司 Oledcomm 合作，针对图书馆场景设计了一款 LiFi 发光灯 C-224，能够透过可见光波传输档案至加密软体的装置中。</p><p>C-224 装设有红外线发射器，也能透过不可见光传输档案，即使灯光熄灭，还是能够使用 Li-Fi。台灯由铝材制成，搭配 Plexiglass Satinice 扩散器平均分散光源，每一组台灯都有 4 个传输热点。</p><p>Picciotto 指出，扩散器的形状设计，是希望光和 Li-Fi 网络覆盖整个桌面，不过目前 Li-Fi 技术上还是有困难，包括无法穿越墙壁、户外使用会受太阳光干扰等缺点，目前还无法普及应用。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018072600344225EfiFQluMx7Ch3T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726003443QC3m5WjBrs1Ao4i2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.324873\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180726003443xGdByiFnmuKCe7Dj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.496616\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/07/24/c-224-lamp-lifi-technology-alexandre-picciotto-ecal-design/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}